NK036(chi)032:1: // 'khrul zhig sangs rgyas dbon po'i rnam thar nyid kyi
NK036(chi)032:2: mdzad pa nor bu'i gsal byed ces bya ba ba
NK036(chi)032:3: zhugs so // dgongs klong mkha' ltar dag pa chos sku'i nam mkha' la //
NK036(chi)032:4: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa longs sku'i dkyil 'khor rgyas //
NK036(chi)032:5: sprul pa'i 'od kyis 'gro ba'i mun pa sel mdzad pa //
NK036(chi)032:6: sku gsum mngon gyur drin can bla ma rgyal gyur cig /
NK036(chi)032:7: tshad med pa'i mkhyen rab dang thugs rjes 'gro ba
NK036(chi)032:8: rnams yang dag pa'i lam la 'khrid par mdzad pa'i
NK036(chi)032:9: ded dpon dam pa de las /
NK036(chi)032:10: kho bos yang zab bla na med pa'i gdams pa ma lus pa thob cing /
NK036(chi)032:11: nyams su len cing skal ba dang ldan pa'i gdul
NK036(chi)032:12: bya gcig gnyis tsam la gdams pa'i don gnang bar
NK036(chi)032:13: byed kyin yod pa'i thad du /
NK036(chi)032:14: dad mos dang ldan pa'i bu slob 'ga' zhig gis /
NK036(chi)032:15: kho bo'i rnam thar cung zhig bris gsung pa la brten nas /
NK036(chi)032:16: kho bo'i rnam thar la sogs bkod pa'i 'os can ma yin zhing /
NK036(chi)032:17: log lta can rnams kyis sgrib pa bsags pa'i rkyen du gyur kyang /
NK036(chi)032:18: khong rnams pa'i nan ma thub pa la brten nas /
NK036(chi)032:19: kho bo'i rnam thar nor bu'i gsal byed bkod pa la /
NK036(chi)032:20: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i tshogs dang bcas pa
NK036(chi)032:21: rnams kyis bzod par gsol la thugs rjes 'dzin par
NK036(chi)032:22: zhu zhing / 'dir bcom ldan 'das mgon po 'jam
NK036(chi)032:23: dpal dbyangs kyi rnam 'phrul chos kyi rgyal po khri
NK036(chi)032:24: srong lde'u btsan gyis bzhengs pa'i bsam yas mi 'gyur
NK036(chi)032:25: lhun gyis grub pa'i gtsug lag khang chen po ma
NK036(chi)032:26: ga d+ha rdo rje gdan dang /
NK036(chi)032:27: gnyis su med pa'i yul byang dkar gyi lha sding zhes bya ba ni /
NK036(chi)032:29: kho bo'i skye ba snga ma'i skye sa gtsug lag khang chen po 'di'i byang phyogs na /
NK036(chi)032:30: sangs rgyas ma chags pad+ma can gyis byin gyis brlabs
NK036(chi)032:31: pa'i byang chub sems bskyed gling zhes bya ba'i bya
NK036(chi)032:33: pha ni sba kun dga' rgyal mtshan ces bya ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:34: ma ni dam mo dad pa skyed ces bya ba'i
NK036(chi)032:35: bur skyes shing der yang las kyi dbang gis chos
NK036(chi)032:36: la mi tshud pa'i rigs su 'dug pa /
NK036(chi)032:37: dkon mchog gi thugs rje la brten nas lo bdun brgyad kyi dus su tshe'i dus byas te /
NK036(chi)032:38: yang de kha'i gang la gdangs 'brel /
NK036(chi)032:39: pha dge bsnyen pad+ma skyabs bya ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:40: ma 'brom mo skyid pa legs zhes bya ba'i bur skyes nas /
NK036(chi)032:41: bu kho bo gcig pu las med pa'i stabs kyis chos sgor mi 'jug cing /
NK036(chi)032:42: 'jig rten gyi bya ba la 'jug bsam pa yod
NK036(chi)032:43: na yang nga rang tshe sngon gyi las bsam pa
NK036(chi)032:45: drin can bla ma dam pa rnams kyi thugs rje la brten nas /
NK036(chi)032:46: lo lnga'i steng du khyi smyon gyis nyi ma gung mthil la rmugs pas /
NK036(chi)032:47: kho bo bstan pa'i sgor 'jug pa'i 'dren pa'i bla mar de byung zhing /
NK036(chi)032:48: gzhan yang kho bo chung ngu nas /
NK036(chi)032:49: dad mos ldan pa zhig yod pa la brten te /
NK036(chi)032:50: dbyar gyi dus su gtsug lag khang chen por phyogs
NK036(chi)032:51: nas gdan drangs pa'i mkhan po dung stong bzhi la
NK036(chi)032:52: sogs pa rnams kyis gtor ma gtong ba'i gtor skad
NK036(chi)032:53: btang ba de thos pa la brten nas /
NK036(chi)032:54: kho bos yang dran pa sad pa snyam byed de /
NK036(chi)032:55: phor chung rer chu thig pa re dang /
NK036(chi)032:56: rtsam pa phum re blugs nas dgong mo sa rub mtshams su nam mkha' la gtor /
NK036(chi)032:57: gtor ma la 'byon par zhu zer ba'i skad ring gsum gsum nam mkha' la gtong dus /
NK036(chi)032:58: nam mkha' la bla ma yin dam mkha' 'gro bzhugs pa snyam byed cing /
NK036(chi)032:60: 'jigs zhum pa zhud tshil pa yang byung /
NK036(chi)032:61: de'i dus dad pa mos gus dang /
NK036(chi)032:62: snying rje chen po yang bongs la bstun pa'i chen po yod pa la brten nas /
NK036(chi)032:63: lo bdun gyi steng du mkhan chen shes rin dang /
NK036(chi)032:64: slob dpon lha shes rab rgyal mtshan pa'i drung du dge tshul gyi bslab pa blangs shing /
NK036(chi)032:65: bstan pa'i sgor zhugs nas dad pa dang shes rab 'thad rab yod pa la /
NK036(chi)032:66: kho bo'i slob chung gcig gi spun la dbang phyug zer ba zhig la mdze byung nas /
NK036(chi)032:67: de'i g.yog rgyug pa la sogs thams cad byas pas /
NK036(chi)032:69: shes rab thams cad des 'grib nas /
NK036(chi)032:70: shes rab snying po 'dzin pa la zla ba gsum gyi bar du slob dpon gyis rgyugs blangs /
NK036(chi)032:72: slob dpon gyis brdungs pa'i skyel ma yang mdze pho des byas pas /
NK036(chi)032:73: shes rab je chung la song zhing /
NK036(chi)032:74: de dus phar phyin la slob gnyer zhig byas pas kyang /
NK036(chi)032:75: shes rab med pa'i stobs kyis /
NK036(chi)032:76: rang sbyong la mi ma mgu pa zhig byung lags shing /
NK036(chi)032:77: de dus bla ma sh+aakya rin chen pa'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:78: 'jam dbyangs dkar po dpa' bo gcig pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:81: 'jam dpal smra seng dang bcas pa rnams kyi lung
NK036(chi)032:82: zhus nas brang 'jam dbyangs dkar po la mos pa
NK036(chi)032:83: byung ste / de la bsnyen pa byas pas /
NK036(chi)032:84: des byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtags la /
NK036(chi)032:85: sngar med pa'i byams pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:86: snying rje rgyud la dungs pa skye ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:87: nub gcig gi rmi lam na yang /
NK036(chi)032:88: mi dkar po zhig gis shel gyi phreng ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:90: ldum ra zhig gi nang na me tog tsam pa ka dkar la dwangs pa'i khrod nas /
NK036(chi)032:91: me tog phor pa tsam 'thu ba la sogs pa rmis pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:92: kho bos yig cha 'dzin pa la tshig rkang gnyis gnyis tsam las mi zin pa de la /
NK036(chi)032:93: yug kha gras kyis yig phreeng bdun phreng gi shog log re tsam zin pa byung bas /
NK036(chi)032:94: de la brten nas slob gnyer ci nus su byed
NK036(chi)032:95: kyin yod pa'i thad nas yi dam de'i thugs rje
NK036(chi)032:96: la brten nas / snying rje dang dag snang chen po rgyud la skyes pa'i mthus /
NK036(chi)032:97: bstan pa rin po che'i rtsa lag mkhan chen rin po che bsod nams grags pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:98: mkhan chen rin po che bsod nams bzang po dpon slob gnyis kyi drung du /
NK036(chi)032:101: 'dul ba la sogs pa rnams kyang nyan cing /
NK036(chi)032:102: gzhan yang rta mgrin dang sgrol ma la sogs pa /
NK036(chi)032:103: bka' gdam lha bzhi la sogs pa'i lung dang /
NK036(chi)032:104: mdor na bya spyod kyi lha mang rabs kyi lung thob cing /
NK036(chi)032:105: mkhyen rab dang thugs rjee'i bdag nyid mkhan chen rin po che bu ston kha che'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:106: slob dpon gzhon bzang gis zhus pa'i zhar la /
NK036(chi)032:107: sa skya ba'i bla ma'i rnal 'byor thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:108: yum chen mo'i sgrub thabs dang /
NK036(chi)032:109: thugs rje chen po dpal mo lugs /
NK036(chi)032:111: yum du sgrub pa dang bcas pa rnams thob cing bla ma sh+aakya rin chen pa'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:112: snga phyi bar gsum dril te thob pa la /
NK036(chi)032:114: gshed dmar lha lnga'i dbang bskur /
NK036(chi)032:115: rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi dbang bskur /
NK036(chi)032:116: n+aa ro mkha' spyod kyi byin rlabs /
NK036(chi)032:117: rtsa dbu ma'i khrid dang bcas /
NK036(chi)032:118: bcom ldan 'das ye shes khyung khra'i sgrub thabs /
NK036(chi)032:119: rta mgrin drag po sum sbrags kyi sgrub thabs /
NK036(chi)032:120: phyag rdor ras chung lugs kyi dbang sgrub thabs dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)032:121: sbyor ba yan lag drug gi thog mar dge ba //
NK036(chi)032:123: tha mar dge ba dang bcas pa'i khrid /
NK036(chi)032:124: kun mkhyen rin po che jo nang pa'i lugs kyi khrid lung dang /
NK036(chi)032:125: spyod yul sras brgyud kyi skor la stod pa dbang
NK036(chi)032:126: rgyal gyi khrid lung o rgyan bsnyen sgrub kyi khrid
NK036(chi)032:127: gegs sel gdams pa dang bcas pa ma lus pa
NK036(chi)032:128: thob / gzhan yang bskyed rim rdzogs rim la sogs pa mang du thob /
NK036(chi)032:129: bla ma ye rgyal ba'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:130: spyod yul chos kha tshang ba ngang gzhan yang nges don gyi khrid dang /
NK036(chi)032:131: yi dam lha'i lung mang du thob /
NK036(chi)032:132: mkhan chen rin po che gzhon nu mgon po'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:133: khro phu ba'i lugs kyi man ngag brgya rtsa /
NK036(chi)032:135: sgrub thabs brgya rtsa la sogs pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:137: jo bo'i lugs kyi gtor lung rgya mtsho la sogs pa'i man ngag du ma thob cing /
NK036(chi)032:138: mkhan chen rin po che grags pa rgyal mtshan pa'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:146: a mo g+ha p+aa sha'i rgyud dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)032:147: rnam thos sras kyi rjes gnang /
NK036(chi)032:148: thugs rje chen po'i dmar khrid /
NK036(chi)032:149: blo sbyong la sogs pa mang du thob cing /
NK036(chi)032:150: gzhan yang de'i dus bdag la shes rab cung zad skyes pa'i mthus /
NK036(chi)032:151: nan tan la gtso cher byas nas /
NK036(chi)032:152: chos rje 'gro ba'i mgon po bsod nams rgyal mtshan pa'i drung nas /
NK036(chi)032:153: chos 'khor chen po'i gsos rnams zhabs tog la sogs pa phun sum tshogs pa legs par bsgrubs nas /
NK036(chi)032:154: bya lo zla ba dang po'i tshes gsum nas sta gon btsugs shing /
NK036(chi)032:155: tshes bco lnga'i nyin par rab tu gnas pa'i dngos gzhi mdzad /
NK036(chi)032:156: tshes bcu bdun la mjug gi cho ga legs par
NK036(chi)032:157: rdzogs par mdzad pa'i tshes bco brgyad kyi nyin par
NK036(chi)032:158: chos kyi rje rin po che bsod nams rgyal mtshan
NK036(chi)032:160: bstan pa'i gsal byed bla ma gung pa la sogs pa /
NK036(chi)032:162: gtsang phyogs kyi bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen pa bzang rigs thams cad 'tshogs pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:163: mkhan chen rin po che zul phu ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:164: dga' ldan pa blo gros seng ges dbu mdzad dbu
NK036(chi)032:165: ru stod smad kyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen pa bzang
NK036(chi)032:167: spyan mnga' grags pa rgyal mtshan pas gtso mdzad dbu
NK036(chi)032:168: ru lung pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen bzang rags tshogs
NK036(chi)032:169: pa mdor na tshogs pa rgya mtsho lta ba'i dbus
NK036(chi)032:170: su / pha rol tu phyin pa la thos pa'i bya ba'i che ba dbyung zhing /
NK036(chi)032:171: nyan bshad byed pa'i dga' ston la dmigs te /
NK036(chi)032:172: bdag cag la bzung 'chang la sogs pa cher med kyang /
NK036(chi)032:173: drin can bla ma rnams kyi thugs rje dang /
NK036(chi)032:174: mched grogs gong ma nye 'brel rnams kyis thugs la btags pa la brten nas /
NK036(chi)032:175: mang ja 'bul nod dang bcas pa legs par bsgrubs nas /
NK036(chi)032:176: nyan bshad byed pa la dmigs nas /
NK036(chi)032:177: chos grwa chen po rtse thang du phyin te /
NK036(chi)032:178: drung 'jam dbyangs sh+aakya rgyal mtshan pa'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:179: phar tshad 'dul ba mngon pa la sogs pa nyan cing /
NK036(chi)032:180: slob dpon dpal rgyal ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:181: slob dpon pan+di ta'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:183: phar phyin gyi don thams cad lhongs par go ba yang byung /
NK036(chi)032:184: chos rje rin po che mon phyogs nas yar 'brog tu phyags phebs /
NK036(chi)032:185: lho phyogs nas phebs pa'i sku skyos la skyi g.yor la sogs pa'i dgon sde rnams su /
NK036(chi)032:186: mang ja 'bul nod la sog pa mdzad nas /
NK036(chi)032:187: de rnams 'grub pa'i gtam snyan skyel ba la 'gro dus dge bshes kun dga' dpal bo rnams kyis /
NK036(chi)032:189: chos rje mjal ba la 'gro ba 'thad gsung nas /
NK036(chi)032:190: nged kyis kyang mjal ba la phyin /
NK036(chi)032:191: nged rang gi bshar gsang byas pa'i sku skal dang /
NK036(chi)032:192: phyags phebs pa'i shangs len la /
NK036(chi)032:193: sku mkhor sum brgya tsam du 'dug pa la /
NK036(chi)032:196: gzhan yang gang 'os kyi 'bul ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:197: dge bdun so so'i phyag tu dar kha re'i 'gyed dang bcas pa bsgrubs nas bsdad yod dus /
NK036(chi)032:198: bla ma bzod pas dbu mdzad /
NK036(chi)032:199: gros la dbang ba rnams kyis nged la zhal ta byon pa la /
NK036(chi)032:200: da lta sha ba rwa co'i 'bogs mtshams su 'dug pas /
NK036(chi)032:201: khyod kyis chos rje'i nye gnas gyis /
NK036(chi)032:202: shar yang khyod rang tsha ba yin gsung pa la /
NK036(chi)032:203: nged kyis zhu ba byas nas /
NK036(chi)032:204: mi ltog gi gces phrug gang yang mi shes /
NK036(chi)032:205: mthong goms la sogs ci yang med pa'i skyid de bar bsdad pas /
NK036(chi)032:206: 'di 'dra'i zhabs tog mi yong lags shing /
NK036(chi)032:207: nga'i mgo 'don byas pa mi yong bar /
NK036(chi)032:208: mgo smod pa 'dra ba zhig las mi yong bas khyed rnams kyis zhu nas /
NK036(chi)032:209: nga rang rgyags kha se mda' re tsam khyer nas /
NK036(chi)032:210: phyags phyir 'brangs nas gdams ngag gi zhun mthar chod
NK036(chi)032:211: pa zhig byung na thugs la btags de ma byung
NK036(chi)032:212: na / dad pa can gyi dkor zas kyis tshos nas sems la 'dre zhugs nas /
NK036(chi)032:213: lus ngag yid gsum gyis bya ba gang min byas nas /
NK036(chi)032:214: ma jo btsun ma la sogs pa la byi phrug bton pa la sogs pa byung na /
NK036(chi)032:215: chos rje rin po che'i zhabs 'dren /
NK036(chi)032:216: nged rang gi mgo smad du song nas 'di phyi
NK036(chi)032:217: gnyis ka'i 'dun ma 'chor ba las mi yong bas
NK036(chi)032:218: / de 'dra mi gsung bar zhu byas /
NK036(chi)032:219: nga rang gis thag bcad ma nyan pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:220: chos rje rin po che'i drung nas kyang thugs rjes bzung nas de mi 'thad /
NK036(chi)032:221: na so gzhon pas da dung slob gnyer gyis gsung nas zhal ta bzang po dang /
NK036(chi)032:222: dapalaldana a ti sha'i thugs dam spyan ras gzigs kyi sku li ma gcig /
NK036(chi)032:223: gdung khang pad spungs dang bcas pa gcig /
NK036(chi)032:225: brgyad stong 'grel chen dbu zhwa na bza' bzhugs gdan dang bcas pa gnang nas /
NK036(chi)032:226: na so gzhon pa la slob gnyer gyis mtshan nyid
NK036(chi)032:227: pa 'di dad pa chung bas blo chud zos la
NK036(chi)032:228: ma song bar mig mar lta ma byed par yar
NK036(chi)032:229: lta gyis la blo chos dang mthun par gyis /
NK036(chi)032:230: de ltar byas nas rang la khebs che zhing gzhan la phan par yong gsung /
NK036(chi)032:231: de dus chos rje'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:232: rdzogs pa chen po gsang ba thig le'i skor /
NK036(chi)032:233: khrid rgyab chos su snyan brgyud yi ge can dang
NK036(chi)032:234: yi ge med pa la sogs pa'i rgyud man ngag
NK036(chi)032:235: bcas pa ma lus par zla ba gsum gyi bar
NK036(chi)032:236: du gnang / gzhan yang yang dben pa'i dbon po
NK036(chi)032:237: yin zer ba zhig gi zhar la shog gsungs nas
NK036(chi)032:238: du gnang / / tshogs bdag dmar po /
NK036(chi)032:239: tshogs bdag sprel gdong ma dang bcas pa rnams ma lus par thugs la btags /
NK036(chi)032:240: slob gnyer byed pa la 'di tsho la gsol ba thob gsungs nas mi g.yo ba dkar po /
NK036(chi)032:242: 'jam dbyangs a ra pa tsa na /
NK036(chi)032:245: shes rab gsal byed rnams kyi lung dang rjes gnang /
NK036(chi)032:246: byin rlabs dang bcas pa ma lus par gnang /
NK036(chi)032:247: gzhan yang thugs rje chen po rgyal po lugs dang /
NK036(chi)032:248: thugs rje chen po'i skor ma lus pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:249: o rgyan rin po che sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor dang /
NK036(chi)032:250: kun byed rgyal po la sogs sems sde'i skor man ngag tu gnang zhing /
NK036(chi)032:251: gzhan yang gu ru'i thugs sgrub dbang dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)032:252: rdzogs chen mnyam nyid rang grol la sogs ma lus pa thugs la btags /
NK036(chi)032:253: pha rgan dang bsdongs nas bsam yas su slebs /
NK036(chi)032:254: de'i dpyid so rgyal nang du grub thob nam mkha'i snying po'i sgrub khang gi zhol du /
NK036(chi)032:255: zla ba gsum gyi bar du 'phags ma dbyangs can ma la gsol ba btab pas /
NK036(chi)032:256: rmi lam du byin gyis brlabs pa'i mtshan ma 'dra byung zhing /
NK036(chi)032:257: de'i bsnyen po'i kha skong la sbyin sreg gcig nyi shu dgu'i nyin par byas pas /
NK036(chi)032:258: na ma mkha' g.ya' dag pa la sbyin sreg byed pa'i steng du /
NK036(chi)032:259: 'ja' tshon bla res phub pa 'dra ba byung bas
NK036(chi)032:260: de dus bla ma sh+aakya rin chen pa bzhugs pas
NK036(chi)032:261: / rten 'brel legs po yin gsung nas /
NK036(chi)032:262: de nas bzung nas shin tu thugs la 'dogs pa zhig byung /
NK036(chi)032:263: lar ni de dus rmi lam gyi rtags mtshon pa de dang /
NK036(chi)032:264: sems can thams cad la pha ma'i 'du shes /
NK036(chi)032:265: byams snying rje rang shugs kyis skye ba zhig byung /
NK036(chi)032:266: de'i dbyar so rgyal sras rin po che thogs med pa mjal nas /
NK036(chi)032:267: theg pa chen po blo sbyong gi khrid dang /
NK036(chi)032:268: snying po don gsum gyi khrid /
NK036(chi)032:269: de la sogs pa'i bskyed rim dang /
NK036(chi)032:270: rdzogs rim gyi lung ma lus pa thugs la btags /
NK036(chi)032:271: de'i dus su byams pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:272: snying rje nges 'byu nga gi skyo shas drag po skyes nas /
NK036(chi)032:273: khong gi drung du chang mi 'thung ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:275: lus skyes sems can phyir mi 'dor ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:276: mdor na lus ngag yid gsum gyi dge sbyor phran
NK036(chi)032:277: tshegs la sogs pa'i dam bca' du ma dag tu
NK036(chi)032:278: phul bas / blo mi rtag pa rgyud la skyes pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:279: blo sna btsan thabs su thung ba byung bas /
NK036(chi)032:280: slob gnyer gyis kyang 'chi khar mi phan par 'dug
NK036(chi)032:281: bsam nas slob gnyer la yang blo gzhol du song
NK036(chi)032:282: zhing / gzungs kyi dpal ba'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:288: mdor na phran tshegs kyi yi dam lha'i sgrubs thabs ma lus pa thob /
NK036(chi)032:289: chos rje rin po che rang byung rol pa'i rdo
NK036(chi)032:290: rje'i drung du thugs rje chen po rgyal ba rgya
NK036(chi)032:291: mtsho'i lung dang / sku gsum ngo sprod la sogs pa mdor na mang du thob /
NK036(chi)032:292: mkhan chen bsod nams rin chen pa'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:294: sa skya ba'i rgyal sras lam bzang la sogs pa mdor na ma lus pa thob /
NK036(chi)032:295: bla ma kun gzhon pa'i drung du sku gsum ngo sprod /
NK036(chi)032:298: mdo drin lan bsab pa la sogs pa mang dag tu thob cing /
NK036(chi)032:299: bla ma bzod pa'i drung du chos rje rin po
NK036(chi)032:300: ches mdzad pa'i dngul chu'i bcud len gyi thogs drangs
NK036(chi)032:301: / gsung sgros kha 'thor thams cad thob /
NK036(chi)032:302: chos rje pan chen pa'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:303: phyag rgya chen po yi ge bzhi pa /
NK036(chi)032:307: tshe dpag med ras chung lugs kyi sgrub thabs /
NK036(chi)032:308: dbang chog dang bcas pa tshang bar thob /
NK036(chi)032:309: phag mo shes rab gsal byed kyi byin rlabs sgrub thabs dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)032:310: gsar ma lugs kyi bcom ldan 'das kyi skyes rabs /
NK036(chi)032:311: bla ma mar ston grags rgyal gyi drung du /
NK036(chi)032:312: phyag rgya chen po lhan cig skyes sbyor bram ze
NK036(chi)032:313: chen po sa ra ha'i lugs kyi phyag rgya chen
NK036(chi)032:314: po thob / rdzogs chen a ro'i khrid mo che /
NK036(chi)032:315: phyag rgya chen po gag ma la sogs mang dag tu thob /
NK036(chi)032:316: bla ma rtogs ldan shes rab mgon po'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:317: phyag rgya chen po bsam gtan thun chog /
NK036(chi)032:321: gtum mo lus sbyong nyi shu pa /
NK036(chi)032:323: 'bru can rde'u la sogs pa'i dka' thub /
NK036(chi)032:324: bcud len gyi be bum chen mo thob /
NK036(chi)032:325: de nas chos rje rin po che nyid 'bri gung na bzhugs pa /
NK036(chi)032:326: gdan 'dren phyin nas bsam yas su phyags phebs dus khrid ma gyogs par tshugs na yongs gsungs nas /
NK036(chi)032:327: stag lo zla ba bcu gcig pa'i tshe gsum la khrid btsugs nas /
NK036(chi)032:329: phyi tshes bcu bdun gyi nyi ma phyed tsam pa la gshegs dus /
NK036(chi)032:332: snang srid thams cad 'ja' 'od zer gsum gyis khengs /
NK036(chi)032:333: sa g.yos chen po lan mang dag tu byung /
NK036(chi)032:335: sa gzhi thams cad ring bsrel /
NK036(chi)032:337: sku gzugs yi ge lnga la sogs pa gcal bkram
NK036(chi)032:338: nas mi rnams ngo mtshar gyi sa la bkod pa'i
NK036(chi)032:339: dus / drung du bzhugs pa rnams kyis zhal ta thugs rjes 'dzin par zhu zhus pas /
NK036(chi)032:340: zhal ta mang pos ci byed /
NK036(chi)032:341: dngos po gang 'dug gi mnga' mi mo skyid pa
NK036(chi)032:342: lags zhes pa'i 'di la sprul sku grags pa 'od
NK036(chi)032:344: byed pa yin mod gsungs nas zhal ta gzhan ma gnang zhing /
NK036(chi)032:345: lar khyed tsho'i lhag byung na skyid pa lags la nyer len gcig ltos gsung pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:346: dge ba'i sa de ga na 'dug /
NK036(chi)032:347: 'dug na 'dir shog gyis gsungs pa'i zhal ta thengs
NK036(chi)032:348: gnyis gsum du gnang ba yin na'ang drung na bzhugs
NK036(chi)032:350: dge bshes kun dga' dpal la sogs pa rnams kyis /
NK036(chi)032:351: bla ma sh+aakya rin chen pa'i phyogs 'dir byas nas nged la ni zhal ta ma bsgyur /
NK036(chi)032:352: de steng stod smad kyi yon bdag grwa pa bu
NK036(chi)032:353: slob yod pa gros la dbang ba rnams 'dus pa'i
NK036(chi)032:354: dus su / nged rang la'ang rngan chen che ba la sogs bsam yas pa rnams kyis byas pas /
NK036(chi)032:355: gzhan rnams kyis de bzhin du byas byung bas /
NK036(chi)032:356: mi go ma chod thing nge ba las med lags shing /
NK036(chi)032:357: thams cad kyis lkugs rnag zer ba'i dus su nga
NK036(chi)032:358: rang gi rtog pa la dpal kun tu bzang po'i
NK036(chi)032:359: rgyal tshab chos kyi rje rin po che la 'di
NK036(chi)032:361: nga la gzhan gang gis kyang ci byed /
NK036(chi)032:362: 'jig rten gyi bya ba thams cad btang nas /
NK036(chi)032:363: mi khyu nas bud pa byas te /
NK036(chi)032:364: ngo mi shes pa'i sa phyogs su phyin nas /
NK036(chi)032:365: dpon por bla ma dkon mchog spyi bor khur /
NK036(chi)032:366: kha drag tu kha nyen dbang chung la rgyab gtad /
NK036(chi)032:369: sprang po ltar gang gis kyang mthong tshor med par byas te /
NK036(chi)032:370: tshe gcig gi sgrub pa nan tan snying por ma byas na /
NK036(chi)032:371: gzhan gang gis kyang phan par mi 'dug pa la /
NK036(chi)032:372: da nga 'di tsho'i gseb tu ci byed bsam pa byung bas /
NK036(chi)032:373: khong rnams kyi khrod du ma bzhugs pas /
NK036(chi)032:374: 'dis log men yin pa 'dra ba'i thugs dgongs byung nas /
NK036(chi)032:375: nga la shog gsungs pa'i zhal ta 'byon kyin 'dug pas /
NK036(chi)032:377: gal te khong rnams pa'i thugs dang 'gal ba byas pas kyang mi yong /
NK036(chi)032:378: lar ngas der phyin kyang gzhan gyi zhabs tog ni mi yong ste /
NK036(chi)032:379: pur gyi zhabs tog tsam zhig byung na bsam nas /
NK036(chi)032:380: khong rnams pa'i khrod du phyin /
NK036(chi)032:381: mi nga rang la blo gros dang dngos po la
NK036(chi)032:382: sogs pa 'don rgyu yod pa der ni mi 'dug
NK036(chi)032:383: / 'dir yong ba la pur gyi zhabs tog tsam zhig byung na /
NK036(chi)032:384: thugs la 'dogs par zhu zer ba zhus pas bla ma rin po che gu ru ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:385: bla ma rin po che rtse dpon slob gnyis dang /
NK036(chi)032:386: zul phu gnas kyi a khu ston pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:387: ston pa grags rdor la sogs pa mdor na stod
NK036(chi)032:388: smad kyi yus po che rnams zhabs tog byed zer
NK036(chi)032:389: / khong rnams pa yang ma 'cham pa'i skabs su /
NK036(chi)032:390: a khu ston pas kha rdol byas nas /
NK036(chi)032:391: da 'di rigs la mi 'cham pa byas pas kyang mi yong /
NK036(chi)032:392: sus zhabs tog byas kyang byin rlabs ma gtogs /
NK036(chi)032:393: bza' yang ba de yang min pas 'di'i 'thad 'os sus bltas kyang /
NK036(chi)032:394: kho rang dpon po'i 'os yin pas kho rang byed du chugs gsung nas kha phud byung bas /
NK036(chi)032:395: nga rang gi lus sems la yang sa dang po thob pa'i bde ba tsam rnyed byung ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:396: khong rnam pa tsho ma 'cham pa de bdag gi grogs su byung nas /
NK036(chi)032:397: pur gyi zhabs tog bya chog pa byung bas /
NK036(chi)032:398: de'i byin brlabs kyis nged rang la grogs med na'ang /
NK036(chi)032:399: da bar skyid po byas pa yin /
NK036(chi)032:400: de nas chos rje rin po che'i gshegs rdzongs /
NK036(chi)032:401: phyogs kyis ja bkol rnams bsgrubs pa'i bar der /
NK036(chi)032:402: bdag gi pha rgan yun ring /
NK036(chi)032:403: zug gzer che ba byas nas /
NK036(chi)032:404: cis kyang phan ma thogs par 'das /
NK036(chi)032:405: kho bos shul du dge ba dge gzhug la sogs mi la ngo mi tsha tsam bsgrubs /
NK036(chi)032:406: nges 'byung dang skyo shas mi rtag pa snying nas tshe 'di'i zhen pa log pa tsam zhig byung /
NK036(chi)032:407: de'i bar der chos rje rin po che'i nang rten /
NK036(chi)032:408: mchod khang sogs bzhengs pa la /
NK036(chi)032:409: lus ngag yid gsum la zol med kyi thil blangs nas /
NK036(chi)032:410: zhabs tog la 'bungs te brtsigs pa las /
NK036(chi)032:411: sdig pa dag pa'i rtags la sogs pa yang mang dag tu byung /
NK036(chi)032:412: lus sems la yang tshe 'di'i snang ba log pa'i nyams than thun yang skyes /
NK036(chi)032:413: nang rten mchod khang dang bcas pa bar chad med par grub /
NK036(chi)032:415: bdag gi ma rgan mo yang gcong nad drag po zhig gis zin nas /
NK036(chi)032:416: zla ba drug tsam gyi bar du nad pa ska rags can nyam thag pa byung zhing /
NK036(chi)032:417: de nas zla ba bdun gyi bar du gdan la
NK036(chi)032:418: 'byar nas bsgul bskyod la sogs pa gang yang mi
NK036(chi)032:419: shes pa / kha ru sing po phye btab pa
NK036(chi)032:420: hub re ma gtogs pa gang yang mi 'gro ba
NK036(chi)032:421: shes pa / / de yang 'thung mi shes par kho bos snyug sbubs ring po bcas nas /
NK036(chi)032:422: de khar bcug nas byin pas shes tsam byung /
NK036(chi)032:423: de'i dus su nged rang la spun zla dang a
NK036(chi)032:424: lce sring mo med par mi gcig po lag gcig
NK036(chi)032:425: tu song bas / lus ngag gi thog tu nyin mtshan gnyis kha sbyor spyod re che byung yang /
NK036(chi)032:426: sems thog tu khyod 'dra ba yong ba /
NK036(chi)032:427: lus la na tsha ni med /
NK036(chi)032:428: rang bzhin gyis g.yog byas pas chog pa 'di la khyod sdug bsngal 'di 'dra yong bas /
NK036(chi)032:429: snying mi bzod pa 'dug lar skyon che ma rgan mo 'di'i khong pa'i nang du zla ba dgu /
NK036(chi)032:430: ngo dang bcu'i bar du khur sbyong spyod dpag tu med pa byas /
NK036(chi)032:431: skyes nas kyang sna khas 'phyi ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:432: shu shu lag pas 'phyi ba la sogs pas byas /
NK036(chi)032:433: gsos bskyangs byas pa'i drin chen yin pa la /
NK036(chi)032:434: da 'di 'dra'i skyo ngal mi bzod pa khyod 'dra ba yod pa bsam nas /
NK036(chi)032:435: des rkyen byas nas sems can thams cad la byams pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:436: snying rje chen po skye ba'i rkyen byas pas ma rgan mo drin che bar byung /
NK036(chi)032:437: de nas ma rgan mo 'das nas rjes kyi bya ba rnams bsgrubs /
NK036(chi)032:438: lcags zad brdar zad la song ba'i stabs kyis pur de sbyin sreg gcig byed rgyu yang ma byung /
NK036(chi)032:439: pur de dur khrod du gdan drangs dus ltas khyad par can byung /
NK036(chi)032:440: bla ma rdor bsam der bzhag nas /
NK036(chi)032:441: khyed kyis khyi byung na srungs /
NK036(chi)032:442: byas zos zin pa dang rus pa dum zhig khyer byon /
NK036(chi)032:443: tsha tsha'i khrod du gtong ba yin byas khong gis thod pa dum bu gcig khyer byon /
NK036(chi)032:444: zla mchod kyi dus la babs pas /
NK036(chi)032:445: de dus bla ma ras pa bzhugs pas /
NK036(chi)032:446: tsha tsha 'debs pa la thod pa de khong gis
NK036(chi)032:447: bsregs nas thod pa de tshig nas bstan byung bas
NK036(chi)032:448: / 'di tsha tsha'i khrod du gtong ba mi drag
NK036(chi)032:449: par 'dug rdo rje phag mo'i sku byon 'dug pa
NK036(chi)032:450: / gsung / bltas pas phag mo'i sku ya mtshan
NK036(chi)032:451: pa gcig byon 'dug tsha tsha btab nas gdang rus
NK036(chi)032:452: ni de'i khrod du ma btang /
NK036(chi)032:453: chos rje rin po che gshegs /
NK036(chi)032:454: pha rgan dang ma rgan gnyis 'das pas /
NK036(chi)032:455: blo sna btsan thabs su log pa kha 'dra gcig kyang byung /
NK036(chi)032:456: yang mi thams cad kyis kha gsag la sogs pa yang btang bas /
NK036(chi)032:457: 'tshe ba 'dra ba zhig kyang byung bas /
NK036(chi)032:459: pha ma gnyis kyi dge ba la dmigs nas gser zho gang gi mar khyer /
NK036(chi)032:460: lha sar jo bo rin po che mjal pa la phyin /
NK036(chi)032:461: lha sa ra mo ches bzhi sde khang na zhang
NK036(chi)032:462: rin po che'i sku 'dra ga cig yod pa'i drung
NK036(chi)032:463: der nyal sa byas kyin mtshan dus gsol ba btab
NK036(chi)032:464: / nyin jo sh+aaka rnam gnyis la gsol ba btab /
NK036(chi)032:467: nub gcig gi rmi lam na /
NK036(chi)032:468: jo bo mi bskyod rdo rje'i phyag g.yas pa'i phyag mdzub gcig la 'jibs pas /
NK036(chi)032:469: 'o ma lta bu'i bdud rtsi'i rgyun lhug lhug byung bas /
NK036(chi)032:470: lus sems bde la sems gzung 'dzin dang bral ba'i
NK036(chi)032:471: nyams khyad par can byung ba de'i ngang la gnyid
NK036(chi)032:472: sad dus yang / yun rin por de'i nyams de dang ma bral ba zhig byung /
NK036(chi)032:474: bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen pa rnams kyi drung
NK036(chi)032:475: du zab don gyi chos zhu ba la dka' las
NK036(chi)032:477: de nas bsam yas su slebs te /
NK036(chi)032:478: dgos med rgyud la skye ba snyam pa zhig byung bas /
NK036(chi)032:479: ston bsod snyoms la yang mi 'gro ba'i grabs gcig byas tsa na /
NK036(chi)032:481: bsod snyoms la phyin pa drag zer rdo yan bsam yas man la phyin pas /
NK036(chi)032:482: nas khal lnga tsam gcig rnyed /
NK036(chi)032:483: des mi'i longs spyod byas nas /
NK036(chi)032:484: da yul la zhen pa byas kyang dgos pa med pas /
NK036(chi)032:485: rgyus med kyis char 'gro dgos bsam nas /
NK036(chi)032:486: la phar rgyab la 'gro ba'i lam la zhugs dus /
NK036(chi)032:488: zla bo med par ma 'gro bsdad pa drag zer dus /
NK036(chi)032:489: dang po a ma'i de nas yong tsa na yang zla bo dang gos med du yong ba yin /
NK036(chi)032:490: da bzhag 'chi ba'i dus su yang zla bo dang gos med gcig pur 'gro ba yin pa la /
NK036(chi)032:491: zla bos ga na langs byas /
NK036(chi)032:492: ras kyi glang ru gcig yod pa de khur nas
NK036(chi)032:493: phyin pa'i sgo 'gag tu shar sgo pa'i yon bdag
NK036(chi)032:494: dge bsnyen gyi nu bo don yod bzang po zer
NK036(chi)032:495: ba de phye rkyal ba chen po khur nas byung
NK036(chi)032:497: rten 'brel shin tu bzang byas nas dbur stod ngos la phyin nas grog nang du sleb dus /
NK036(chi)032:498: bla ma o rgyan pa'i drung du mjal du 'gro dgos snyam pa la /
NK036(chi)032:499: bla ma o rgyan pa 'bri gung la bzhud nas /
NK036(chi)032:500: mi bzhugs zer ba gcig thos pas /
NK036(chi)032:501: der o rgyan la ma phyin par /
NK036(chi)032:502: chos rje pan chen pa'i drung du 'gro bsam nas /
NK036(chi)032:504: stod ya gi nas mar la byis pa sil po
NK036(chi)032:505: khur ba gcig byung bas rten 'brel gcig brtag dgos
NK036(chi)032:507: sil po de yang gci ba gser kha ma gcig
NK036(chi)032:508: gis ltem gyis khengs 'dug khyod la ming ci zer
NK036(chi)032:509: byas pas / gu ru skyabs zer ba yin zer bas /
NK036(chi)032:510: rten 'brel bzang bsam nas yar 'dzegs la kha der slebs dus /
NK036(chi)032:512: mos gus thun mong ma yin pa zhig der skyes nas yar phyin dus /
NK036(chi)032:513: nged rang gi grogs mched rtse thang pa /
NK036(chi)032:514: sngon la slebs pa tshos ngo shes nas /
NK036(chi)032:515: chos nyid rang grol zer ba gcig yod pa bsu ba la btang byung bas /
NK036(chi)032:516: rten 'brel bzang snyam sems spro sing ba zhig byung /
NK036(chi)032:517: grogs mched rnams kyis kyang chos rje mjal ma zin par 'dug pas /
NK036(chi)032:518: nga slebs pa dang dgongs ja'i thog tu mjal ba
NK036(chi)032:519: la phyin pas chos rje'i drung nas dgyes tshor chen
NK036(chi)032:520: po yang mdzad / gang dgos kyi chos la sogs pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:521: sgos su phag mo shes rab gsal byed kyi byin rlabs /
NK036(chi)032:522: rjes gnang dang bcas pa thugs rjes bzung /
NK036(chi)032:523: de nas o rgyan du phyin /
NK036(chi)032:524: bla ma rin po che o rgyan pa mjal /
NK036(chi)032:525: dgyes tshor la sogs pa chen po mdzad /
NK036(chi)032:526: de dus stod smad kyi grwa pa thams cad bsod snyoms dang /
NK036(chi)032:528: dgon pa so gsod par 'dug pas /
NK036(chi)032:529: bsnyen sgrub gcig byas na bsam /
NK036(chi)032:530: bcom ldan 'das phag mo'i bsnyen sgrub zla ba gsum
NK036(chi)032:531: gyi bar du byas pas thugs rjes 'dzin pa'i rtags
NK036(chi)032:532: rmi lam du cung zad tsam yang byung /
NK036(chi)032:534: rin po che o rgyan pas dgun der rdzogs pa chen po snying thig gi khrid gsung /
NK036(chi)032:535: da lan khyod yod pas lhag lus med par gnang dgos gsung nas /
NK036(chi)032:536: lhag ma ma lus pa rdzogs par gnang zhing /
NK036(chi)032:538: rgyab chos yang tig dang bcas pa yang gnang /
NK036(chi)032:539: bskang gso'i lung dang las byang gi lung /
NK036(chi)032:540: lar ni rdzogs pa chen po'i cha lag ma lus pa /
NK036(chi)032:541: rjes gnang byin rlabs dang bcas pa thugs rjes bzung /
NK036(chi)032:542: dpal n+aa ro pa'i chos drug /
NK036(chi)032:543: rgod tshang pa'i khrid chen brgyad /
NK036(chi)032:544: zab mo lnga ldan gyi khrid /
NK036(chi)032:545: gzhan yang chos rje 'jig rten mgon po'i 'khrungs chos la sogs pa mang dag tu gnang /
NK036(chi)032:546: chos rje 'brug pa'i thub lnga dang /
NK036(chi)032:547: dbu ma'i tshig la sogs pa dbu ma'i lung mang dag tu yang gnang zhing /
NK036(chi)032:548: zla ba lnga'i bar la dngul chu ril bu'i bcud len byas pas /
NK036(chi)032:549: bcud len yang 'byongs po byung ba'i stobs kyis lus la na tsha med cing /
NK036(chi)032:550: sems gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa dang bral ba'i ngang
NK036(chi)032:551: nas lar sngar phan chad mi tshe don med la
NK036(chi)032:552: bskyal 'dug / da phyin chad tshe 'di'i bya ba
NK036(chi)032:553: snabs bzhin du rgyang btang na phyi ma'i bya ba
NK036(chi)032:554: la gting bsnyab byas nas gcig pur dben pa brten
NK036(chi)032:557: tshong so nam khe spogs la sogs pa /
NK036(chi)032:558: mdor na chos dang mi mthun pa thams cad skyur la /
NK036(chi)032:559: tshe 'di blos btang nas mi mang gi gral 'go dang /
NK036(chi)032:560: gzhan gyi sha tsha gros 'debs dang /
NK036(chi)032:561: mdor na 'jig rten 'di'i bya ba byed re shi snyam pa'i zhe mna' gting nas bskyal nas /
NK036(chi)032:562: da yul la log pa'i don kyang mi 'dug gangs
NK036(chi)032:563: ti se la phyin nas mi tshe theb por gyi
NK036(chi)032:564: sgrub pa gcig byed dgos snyam pa byung nas /
NK036(chi)032:565: bla ma o rgyan pa'i drung du zhus pa 'bri
NK036(chi)032:566: gung pa'i stod ri'i thems kyi khrod du 'gro bar
NK036(chi)032:567: zhu zhus pas / 'gro ba mi drag gsung nas khong gi btang du ma nyan pas /
NK036(chi)032:568: da bla ma'i bka' bcags pas mi yong bsam nas /
NK036(chi)032:569: ti se la ma phyin par skyid smad la yong nas /
NK036(chi)032:570: 'phan yum lung pa man chad kyi ri khrod dgon pa rnams su gnas gtad /
NK036(chi)032:572: nyan po la sogs pa'i 'phan yul lung pa'i dgon pa rnams ltad mo lta yin /
NK036(chi)032:574: bla ma rnams la'ang bla ma'i rnal 'byor re re tsam /
NK036(chi)032:575: khong rang rnams pa'i dgon pa'i chos lugs dang mthun pa'i chos 'brel re tsam zhus /
NK036(chi)032:576: de nas dge mor chos rje rin po bsam gtan pa'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:577: bla ma'i rnal 'byor ngo sprod dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)032:578: grub thob gcer gyi rnam thar 'khrungs chos dang /
NK036(chi)032:579: chos rje rgya brag pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:580: sangs rgyas sgom pa gnyis kyi rnam thar dang bcas pa zhus /
NK036(chi)032:581: de nas chu 'thung ma gcig la chu 'thung gi lung zhus nas bsam yas su slebs dus /
NK036(chi)032:582: bla ma sh+aakya rin chen pa'i drung du mjal ba
NK036(chi)032:583: la mchims phur phyin pas khyod slebs pa de bzang
NK036(chi)032:584: / da lo dbyar 'dir sdod gsung nas zhal ta bzang po gnang /
NK036(chi)032:586: nga rang la ni nas la sogs rdog po gcig kyang med /
NK036(chi)032:587: 'brel can rnams kyang nas kyi skad ngan 'don kyin 'dug pas /
NK036(chi)032:588: nga la ster dgos pa byung gis dogs pa yin pa 'dra bsam pa'i rnam rtog cig skyes /
NK036(chi)032:589: de bas kyang nga rang chu 'thung ba drag bsam /
NK036(chi)032:590: yang dben gnas kyi gzims khang rnying pa ru /
NK036(chi)032:591: zla ba hril po gsum la chu 'thung pas /
NK036(chi)032:593: nges 'byung dang skyo shas dpag tu med pa skye ba cig byung /
NK036(chi)032:594: lus la bltas tsa na yang rang bzhin gyis dwangs la snum bag dang ldan pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:595: lag pa la bltas pas phyi gsal nang gsal lta bu gcig byung nas /
NK036(chi)032:596: dge sbyor shin tu 'phel ba skyid pa cig byung /
NK036(chi)032:597: de nas dgun so der bla ma sh+aaka rin pa'i zhal ta la 'dir sdod la /
NK036(chi)032:598: rin po che gu ru pa'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:601: rin po che gu ru'i drung du rdzogs chen snying khrid nyan cing /
NK036(chi)032:602: sag ya brag phug tu bsdad pa la mthun rkyen cher med pas nam zla grang ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:603: mi mngas kyi khrod du 'gro ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:604: dka' thub bcud len byed pa mi 'grub par 'dug
NK036(chi)032:605: snyam pas der tshogs chung re tsam byung ba'i zan
NK036(chi)032:606: skam rnams la mkhan po byas nas /
NK036(chi)032:607: zan rdog re la tshal drug drug tu byas nas /
NK036(chi)032:609: tshogs 'khor tshogs chang dang bcas pa rnams kyis 'phral phyir nas /
NK036(chi)032:610: zan skam rkyal chung tsam byung zhing /
NK036(chi)032:611: chos thon nas zan skam rkyal chung gang dang /
NK036(chi)032:612: gtor phye 'gyed mkhan byung ba bsags pas rtsam pa dum gcig yod pa la dmigs rten byas nas /
NK036(chi)032:613: der mtshams dam po byas nas bsdad pa drag par 'dug snyam pa byung /
NK036(chi)032:614: sdod sa mi tshong sir byas na /
NK036(chi)032:615: khong rnam pa'i phud la phar 'bod tshur 'bod dang /
NK036(chi)032:616: bza' btung gi lan mjal res rnams mthong nas dud 'dra te yang ldang ste /
NK036(chi)032:617: dge sbyoor gyi'ang sad du 'gro ba 'dug snyam nas /
NK036(chi)032:618: der mtshams dam po zhig byas nas zla ba gsum gyi bar dge sbyor la zhugs pas /
NK036(chi)032:619: dge sbyor 'phel zhing nyams rtogs rnams kyang ci rigs pa byung /
NK036(chi)032:620: khyad par nub gcig gi rmi lam na gtsang pa
NK036(chi)032:621: bro pa shing rtsed byed pa'i shing btsugs pa'i thag
NK036(chi)032:622: pa gcig la 'jug pa snyam byed pa zhig la
NK036(chi)032:623: skye dman mang po zhig gis thag pa de nas
NK036(chi)032:624: 'then pas nam mkha' la yer khyer pa snyam byed
NK036(chi)032:625: pa zhig la / nam mkha' la phyag na rdo rje'i sku yin snyam pa'am /
NK036(chi)032:626: reg 'ga' sangs rgyas stong bzhugs pa'i thang kha gcig yin pa snyam byed pa gcig la /
NK036(chi)032:627: lus sems la bde stong gi nyams khyad par can skyes /
NK036(chi)032:628: de'i mod la gnyid sad byung lus la bde bas khyab cing /
NK036(chi)032:629: sems la gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa thams cad rang sar dag pa'i ngang nas /
NK036(chi)032:630: brag phug de 'od gsal gyis ltems khengs 'dug pa'i ngang nas /
NK036(chi)032:631: dar cig nas dran pa rnyed tsa na /
NK036(chi)032:633: nang gi 'od gsal 'di yang legs snyam nas /
NK036(chi)032:634: sems la dga' brod kyi 'dzin pa zhig zhugs 'dug pas /
NK036(chi)032:635: de nyid kyi ngang la de nyid bla mar shar nas /
NK036(chi)032:636: a pha khyod 'dra ba yod pa mdangs sum rmi lam gyi nyams dum pa shar ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:637: da lta 'od gsal gyi snang ba cung zad shar ba 'di la de tsam gyi zhen chags /
NK036(chi)032:638: lar chos rje bla ma rin po che'i sku drin la brten nas /
NK036(chi)032:639: chos sku ka dag chen po'i klong yangs nas /
NK036(chi)032:640: longs sku dwangs zhing khams kyi snang ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:641: sprul sku 'gag med chen po'i ngang las /
NK036(chi)032:642: gang shar 'dzin med du rang grol zhing thugs rje byams dang snying rje ma bu gcig pa la /
NK036(chi)032:643: brtse ba lta bu'i sems kyis 'gro la phan pa rgya cher bsgrubs shing /
NK036(chi)032:644: mdor na sku gsum du 'bral med pa'i dgongs pa
NK036(chi)032:645: la dus thams cad du 'bral med nyams su len
NK036(chi)032:647: de lta bu'i nyams len gyi lha re mthong ba la dga' brod rang 'cha' ci dgos /
NK036(chi)032:648: lar skyid pa yin snang srid 'od gsal du shar ba 'di skyid pa yin /
NK036(chi)032:649: gang shar sku gsum du mthong ba 'di skyid pa yin /
NK036(chi)032:650: bla ma rin po che'i sku drin la 'khor thabs mi 'dug pa snyam nas /
NK036(chi)032:651: bla ma la mos gus dpag tu med pa gcig kyang skyes /
NK036(chi)032:653: gang shar lam yin snang srid bla mar shar ba 'di lta bu'i don rtogs pas /
NK036(chi)032:654: ci byas bde bar 'dug snyam pa'i rtogs pa khyad par can cig kyang skyes /
NK036(chi)032:655: de nas zhag phyi ma'i tho rangs kyi rmi lam zhig na /
NK036(chi)032:656: nam langs pa dang nyi ma rtse shar ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:657: nam mkha' nas 'bru'i char pa si li li babs pa zhig rmis pa'i mod /
NK036(chi)032:658: sems kyi thog tu bde ya le ba'i rnam pa zhig la /
NK036(chi)032:659: ngo bo de dga' bar shar ba'i rig 'dra ba 'dug /
NK036(chi)032:660: de mod la gnyid sad tsam na yang /
NK036(chi)032:662: de'i mod la dga' brod kyi bdud zhugs pa ma tshor ba 'dug pa snyam pa'i ngang de la /
NK036(chi)032:663: skyag dad med dga' brod kyi bdud yin du chug ci byas chos /
NK036(chi)032:665: snang srid bla mar shar dus /
NK036(chi)032:666: bde sdug ci byung yang khyad par spu tsam zhig kyang med par /
NK036(chi)032:667: thams cad kun tu bzang po'i rol pa yin par gding chos /
NK036(chi)032:668: de nas de kha'i rjes la ci byung yang 'dra ba yin pa la /
NK036(chi)032:669: nyi ma shar ba de nyid gnas skabs su sdig pa 'dag pa'i rtags yin par go //
NK036(chi)032:670: 'bru'i char babs pa de nyid 'bras bu lam du byed pa'i rtags yin par 'dug pas /
NK036(chi)032:671: bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka' drin yin snyam pa'i mos gus dungs pa zhig kyang skyes /
NK036(chi)032:672: de nas bzung nas lo drug gi bar la /
NK036(chi)032:673: chos rje rin po che gu ru ba'i drung gi thugs rjes bzung nas /
NK036(chi)032:675: mi su la'ang shes 'a brel la sogs med cing /
NK036(chi)032:676: dma' ba'i sa bzung nas bem po stag hral gyis phyi'i 'phyor chas dang /
NK036(chi)032:677: nang gi dge sbyor byed pa'i gos kyi go bcad cing de bar gyi 'tsho ba de /
NK036(chi)032:680: des ma lcogs pa'i bar skabs rnams su dngul chu'i bcud len dang /
NK036(chi)032:681: rtag tu ngu gnyis kyi bcud len la sogs rnams la brten nas bsdad pas /
NK036(chi)032:682: nga rang gi skyid pa'i dge sbyor 'phel ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:683: phyi ltar du snying rje'i gnas dang /
NK036(chi)032:684: nyam thag pa lta bu byung /
NK036(chi)032:685: de'i dus gzhan gyi gral 'gor mi sdod pa la sogs pa byas dus /
NK036(chi)032:686: bla ma rin po che gu ru pa'i drung nas kyang bka' bkyon dang /
NK036(chi)032:687: bla ma bkras dpal ba la sogs rnams kyi dman
NK036(chi)032:688: pa'i chos brgyad 'di 'dras ci byed zer nas bka'
NK036(chi)032:689: bkyon byung yang nga rang la dge sbyor 'phel bar
NK036(chi)032:691: de nas ri mo can dang /
NK036(chi)032:693: bya 'ug lha khang la sogs pa rnams su yang dka' thub byed cing /
NK036(chi)032:694: sgrub pa nan tan snying po byas dus /
NK036(chi)032:695: rmi nyams dang shes nyams dang /
NK036(chi)032:696: snang nyams rnams than thun byung ba rnams yi ge gzhan du shes par bya /
NK036(chi)032:697: de nas rin po che sprul sku pa'i drung lho
NK036(chi)032:698: brag nas phyags phebs te mjal ba la rin po
NK036(chi)032:699: che gu ru ba byon pa'i phyags phyi la phyin
NK036(chi)032:700: nas / rin po che gu ru pa'i drung du
NK036(chi)032:701: yang gsang ba bla na med pa'i snying thig gi
NK036(chi)032:702: thog drangs dbang gang brgyud theg mchog gu ru'i thugs
NK036(chi)032:704: de la sogs pa'i o rgyan gyi gter chos mang dag tu zhus shing thugs la btags /
NK036(chi)032:705: rin po che sprul sku pa'i drung du yang /
NK036(chi)032:707: phyag na rdo rje mdo lugs /
NK036(chi)032:708: phyag na rdo rje gtum po khrag thog /
NK036(chi)032:709: chos rje rin po che'i gsung sgros kha 'thor mang dag tu thugs la btags shing /
NK036(chi)032:710: bdag gi phyi ma'i bla ma dang 'jig rten 'dis pha'i go bcad nas /
NK036(chi)032:711: thugs rjes bu bzhin du skyong /
NK036(chi)032:712: de'i dus su bla ma rin po che stag tshang pa mchims phur byon dus /
NK036(chi)032:713: chos rje yang dgon pa'i lugs kyi lhan cig skyes sbyor /
NK036(chi)032:714: gtum mo zhag bdun ma'i khrid /
NK036(chi)032:715: chos kyi rdo rje'i sba bshad /
NK036(chi)032:716: bar do gnad phreng gi byin rlabs dang bcas /
NK036(chi)032:717: thugs rje chen po'i dmar khrid /
NK036(chi)032:718: lha bcu ma'i dbang bskur sgrub thabs dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)032:719: gzhan yang ri chos kyi cha lag la sogs pa
NK036(chi)032:720: phyag rgya chen po'i chos mang dag tu thugs la
NK036(chi)032:721: btags / bla ma ri khrod pa bya bral ba la /
NK036(chi)032:723: gdams pa dar tshags kyi mgo byas /
NK036(chi)032:724: rgyud phyi ma cha lag dang bcas pa rnams kyi pod lung zhal gdams dang bcas pa gnang /
NK036(chi)032:725: chos kyi rje rin po che bsod nams rgyal mtshan pa'i drung nas mkhan po mdzad /
NK036(chi)032:726: slob dpon many+dzu sh+r+ai pa'i drung nas slob dpon mdzad /
NK036(chi)032:727: mkhan chen bkras sangs pa'i drung nas gsang ston mdzad /
NK036(chi)032:728: lo bco brgyad kyi thog tu bsnyen par rdzoogs pa thob cing /
NK036(chi)032:729: gzhan yang chos rje rin po che ba'i drung du dpal dus kyi 'khor lo /
NK036(chi)032:735: drung pa nyid kyis mdzad pa'i khrid yig rdzogs pa /
NK036(chi)032:738: spyod yul drung pa nyid kyis mdzad pa'i dmar khrid /
NK036(chi)032:739: bde mchog lugs kyi dbang mngon rtogs dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)032:740: chos rje rgyal sras thogs med pas mdzad pa'i bla ma'i rnal 'byor /
NK036(chi)032:742: rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi sgrub thabs /
NK036(chi)032:743: rdo rje dbyangs can dkar mo /
NK036(chi)032:745: tsa rtsi ka'i sgrub thabs la sogs pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:746: chos rje 'phags pas mdzad pa'i man+dala 'bul chog gsol 'debs dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)032:747: bla ma sh+aaka rin pa'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:748: u rgyan bsnyen sgrub gegs sel dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)032:749: ri chos skor gsum dang bcas pa mang dag tu thob cing /
NK036(chi)032:750: mdor na dka' thub dang chu 'thung gi lto go bcad cing /
NK036(chi)032:751: ber po stag ral gyis gos go bcad nas sgrub
NK036(chi)032:752: pa la nan tan snying por byas pa la lcags
NK036(chi)032:753: ri mu khyud kyi nang du /
NK036(chi)032:754: gsang spyod dpyid lo gcig bskyangs pa la /
NK036(chi)032:755: dge sbyor shin tu 'phel zhing lus sems bde ba'i thad nas /
NK036(chi)032:756: bsam yas bar khang du nyal dus nub gcig rmi lam du /
NK036(chi)032:757: dbu rtse stod pad+ma can gyi steng na yod pa snyam byed pa la /
NK036(chi)032:758: mdun gyi nam mkha' la 'od kyi lha mo gsum
NK036(chi)032:759: gar byed cing snyan pa'i glu dbyangs sgrogs pa'i nang
NK036(chi)032:760: la rigs kyi bu snga ma ltar gyis shig /
NK036(chi)032:762: 'ja' ltar yal bar gyur pa'i mod la gnyid sad byung nas /
NK036(chi)032:763: lus la bde stong gi nyams khyad par can dang /
NK036(chi)032:764: sems rtog med kyi ngang du ting nge 'dzin la yun ring du gnas par gyur /
NK036(chi)032:765: lha sar phyin dus gcig tsa na /
NK036(chi)032:766: bla ma sh+aaka rin pa'i drung nas /
NK036(chi)032:767: nged dpon slob gnyis kyis ngo bo rin po che'i lcags sgo'i mdun du /
NK036(chi)032:769: zhi khro'i bskang bshags byas dus /
NK036(chi)032:771: gos chen kha dog gsum bsnol ba'i me tog la mu tig brgyud pa gcig /
NK036(chi)032:772: bdag gi spyi bo'i gtsug tu rang bzhin gyi babs byung bas /
NK036(chi)032:773: bla ma rin po che sh+aaka rin pa'i gsung nas /
NK036(chi)032:775: la nye bzang ba yin gsung nas dgyes tshor chen po mdzad /
NK036(chi)032:776: nged rang la'ang des 'phrod pa bzhin byung bas /
NK036(chi)032:777: mkhan chen rin po che phyogs las rnam par rgyal ba'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:779: sbyor ba yan lag drug gi ngo sprod dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)032:781: thugs rje chen po 'gro ba 'dul ba'i lung dang bcas pa rnams gnang /
NK036(chi)032:782: chos rje kun gzhon pa'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:783: bla ma'i rnal 'byor ngo sprod dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)032:784: skyes mchog chos rje'i gsung sgros kha 'thor ba yang 'ga' gnang /
NK036(chi)032:785: mkhan chen d+har+m+aa sh+r+ai ba'i drung du /
NK036(chi)032:786: blo sbyong thun gcig pa snying po don gsum /
NK036(chi)032:787: gsum pa lo ts+aa dang mkha' 'gro'i brda'i ngo sprod gsung sgros dang bcas pa rnams gnang /
NK036(chi)032:790: sgrol ma dkar mo nang sgrub tu bya ba'i lung thob /
NK036(chi)032:791: slob dpon gzhon nu rdol gyi drung du /
NK036(chi)032:792: ye shes khyung khra'i lung thob /
NK036(chi)032:793: gnod sbyin a par tsit+ta'i sgrub thabs /
NK036(chi)032:794: gzhan yang gcod yul gyi gdams pa'i skor mang du thob /
NK036(chi)032:795: bla ma bsod she pa'i drung du ri chos kyi zab pa'i dbugs bzhi bar do'i gdams pa /
NK036(chi)032:796: bar do byang chub sems kyi khrid /
NK036(chi)032:797: kun tu byang chub sems kyi khrid /
NK036(chi)032:798: kun rdzob byang chub sems kyi khrid /
NK036(chi)032:802: chos rje yang dgon pa'i bka' shog /
NK036(chi)032:803: gtum mo'i 'khrul 'khor nyi shu pa la sogs gdams pa mang dag tu gnang /
NK036(chi)032:804: rin po che chos dbyings pa'i drung du sems khrid yid bzhin nor bu'i khrid /
NK036(chi)032:805: shog dril bzhi'i lung rgyab chos nor bu'i phreng ba /
NK036(chi)032:806: phyag rgya chen po'i sgang dril /
NK036(chi)032:807: zhang rin po che'i bka' 'bum po ti gnyis /
NK036(chi)032:811: gzer lnga zhal kyal ma dang bcas pa gnang /
NK036(chi)032:812: de la sogs pa'i mkhas grub kyi bla ma dam pa rnams mang du bsten cing /
NK036(chi)032:814: gsung gi bdud rtsi myangs nas /
NK036(chi)032:822: mkha' ri mtsho la sogs pa'i dben gnas dang /
NK036(chi)032:824: sngar gyi grub chen gong ma rnams kyis byin gyis
NK036(chi)032:825: brlabs pa'i gnas mchog rnams su sgrub pa'i rgyal mtshan
NK036(chi)032:826: btsugs shing / lto gos la gyong bskur /
NK036(chi)032:829: spyir gyi bstan pa rin po che dang sgos kyi
NK036(chi)032:830: rdzogs pa chen po'i zhabs 'dren du ma song ba
NK036(chi)032:831: byed pa'i khur chen po khur nas sgrub pa nan
NK036(chi)032:833: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro rnams kyis byin rlabs zhugs shing /
NK036(chi)032:834: thugs rjes bzung ba la brten nas lus ngag la'ang
NK036(chi)032:835: nyams dang rtogs pa mtshon re byung ba la dga'
NK036(chi)032:836: brod la sogs pa'i bdud dum pa re zhugs dus
NK036(chi)032:837: / dkon mchog gi thugs rje la brten nas /
NK036(chi)032:839: bdud de kha lam du slong nas /
NK036(chi)032:840: dge sbyor gyi bogs rgyangs pa re yod pa byung zhing /
NK036(chi)032:841: khyad par o rgyan gyi slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas /
NK036(chi)032:842: pan+di ta chen po bi ma la mi tra gnyis
NK036(chi)032:843: kyis thog drangs pa'i grub chen nyi shu rtsa lngas
NK036(chi)032:844: byin gyis brlabs pa'i dben gnas mchims phu dge'u dge
NK036(chi)032:847: ri mo can rnams su drin can rin po che 'od gsal rang grol gyi thugs rjes gzigs /
NK036(chi)032:849: lo drug gi bar sgrub pa'i rgyal mtshan btsugs shing /
NK036(chi)032:850: lo drug gi bar la jo bo bzang nas 'bul mkhan med /
NK036(chi)032:851: snying rje nas ster mkhan med pas nga rang gis kyang lto gos kyi phyir /
NK036(chi)032:852: sdug dogs nas bsod snyoms la sogs pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:853: mda' na mar la 'dod yon gnyer ba la sogs
NK036(chi)032:854: pa ma byas par 'dag 'byar dang ri las mi
NK036(chi)032:855: 'bebs byed pa la dka' thub bcud len tshogs su
NK036(chi)032:856: byung ba'i skal pa rnams la brten cing /
NK036(chi)032:857: gos ber po rtag hral sha 'gag /
NK036(chi)032:858: gnyal tshos dkar por song ba gcig la brten nas bsdad /
NK036(chi)032:859: de dus rin po che gu ru bas thugs la btags kyang /
NK036(chi)032:860: bdag gi dkor lci'i dogs nas rtsam nas /
NK036(chi)032:861: na bza' la sogs pa ci gnang yang ma zhus pa yin /
NK036(chi)032:862: sgrub pa nan tan snying por byas dus /
NK036(chi)032:864: shig gegs la sogs pa byung yang /
NK036(chi)032:865: de rnams thams cad kyang bla ma dkon mchog gi thugs rje dang /
NK036(chi)032:866: nga rang gi mos gus la brten nas lam gyi bogs su song nas /
NK036(chi)032:868: bla ma sh+aaka rin pa bla ma te rtse ba rnams kyis dbu mdzad /
NK036(chi)032:869: dge'u na bzhugs pa'i grwa rogs grogs mched yon bdag
NK036(chi)032:870: pho mo dang bcas pa thams cad kyis thugs rjes
NK036(chi)032:871: gzigs / byams po byas pa la brten nas /
NK036(chi)032:872: a na dge sbyor mi 'phel zhing so ma gsod pa byung bas /
NK036(chi)032:874: bya chu mig la sogs pa'i ri brag dum pa brten cing /
NK036(chi)032:875: lhag par bya chu mig tu bsdad dus lo lnga tsam gyi bar la /
NK036(chi)032:876: dge sbyor 'phel zhing sgyu lus bde ba /
NK036(chi)032:877: nyams dang rtogs pa la sogs kyang ngang gis 'phel
NK036(chi)032:878: bar byung ba'i thad nas yon bdag pho mo la
NK036(chi)032:879: sogs pa than thun gyis tshor nas /
NK036(chi)032:880: sems la phan pa'i gdams ngag kyang than thun ston dgos pa byung zhing /
NK036(chi)032:881: de dag gi thad du lag na ci yang med dus /
NK036(chi)032:882: chos rjee rin po che'i bco brgyad mchod pa byed /
NK036(chi)032:883: gzhan la ster rgyu ma byung tsa na /
NK036(chi)032:884: nga rang gi spol ta phor pa kha mtho ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:886: gtor ma phor pa re la brten nas mchod pa'i go bcad cing /
NK036(chi)032:887: de ring yon bdag pho mo rnams kyis phul ba'i spyad pa rnams chud zos la ma song zhing /
NK036(chi)032:888: don yod par bya ba'i phyir du zla ba byung ngo cog gi bco brgyad mchod pa la /
NK036(chi)032:889: mkha' 'gro chos skyong la gtor tshogs dang /
NK036(chi)032:890: ri khrod na bzhugs pa rnams la tshogs kyi 'khor los mnyes par byas shing /
NK036(chi)032:891: gzhan lo dus kyi bac+wo brgyad mchod pa la /
NK036(chi)032:892: nga rang gang yod du so so'i phyag tu gral
NK036(chi)032:893: 'gyed dang bcas pa bsgrubs pa'i byin brlabs kyis cung
NK036(chi)032:895: than thun byung ba rnams bsam yas 'dus 'tshogs su lo bcag ma'am /
NK036(chi)032:896: lo re bzhin du dge 'dun tshogs pa rgya ma tsho lta bu la bsnyen cing bkur ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:897: de steng rin po che gu ru pa'i drung nas la gsol ba ma thebs pa'i dus /
NK036(chi)032:898: chos rje rin po che de nyid kyi thugs dgongs la /
NK036(chi)032:899: skyid smad la sogs pa'i chos sde rnams su /
NK036(chi)032:900: mang ja 'bul ba dang bcas pa zhig bsgrub nas
NK036(chi)032:901: dgongs pa yod pa la thugs dgongs ma rdzogs par
NK036(chi)032:902: gshegs / da nga rang gi rin po che'i zhabs
NK036(chi)032:903: tog gzhan 'grub pa der ni ma 'dug chos rje
NK036(chi)032:904: rin po che dri med pa'i phyag srool mi nyams
NK036(chi)032:905: gshegs / pa dang / drung pa de nyid kyis
NK036(chi)032:906: kyang thugs dgongs lam lus de 'dra bar de rdzogs
NK036(chi)032:908: bsam yas su bla chen pas gtso mdzad tshogs pa
NK036(chi)032:909: rgya mtsho lta bu la tshar 'gyed dang bcas pa
NK036(chi)032:910: / bla ma bkra shis dpal bas dbu mdzad mchims phu ba rnams la tshogs kyi 'khor lo /
NK036(chi)032:912: ri bo bya chu mig rnams su yang tshogs 'khor 'gyed dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)032:913: skyid smad kyi chos sde rnams su mang ja 'gyed 'bul nod dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)032:914: gung thang me tog mchod pa rtse thang gnyis su mang ja 'bul nod dang bcas pa bsgrubs nas /
NK036(chi)032:915: dad pas sbyin pa chud ma zos pa byas shing /
NK036(chi)032:916: de'i khul nas nga rang gi lus ngag yid gsum dge ba la bskul ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:917: sems can la phan ci thogs mdor na smod smad
NK036(chi)032:918: chu lho byang rnams sa tha na gtor ma phor
NK036(chi)032:919: pa re tsam gyis sems can la phan pa ci
NK036(chi)032:920: 'grub byas shing / rang las cung lhag pa rnams la 'dun pa chen pos mos pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:921: gus pa dpag tu med pas sangs rgyas su bsgoms pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:922: rang dang mnyam par gyur pa rnams la'ang mthos gnan /
NK036(chi)032:923: chags sdang 'gran sems spangs nas dag pa'i snang ba kho na bsgoms /
NK036(chi)032:924: bla ma'i 'du shes su dam bcas pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:925: rang las dman par gyur pa rnams la'ang zhe sdang ba dang /
NK036(chi)032:926: khyad du gsod pa thams cad spangs nas byams pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:927: snying rje phyogs ris med pas /
NK036(chi)032:928: lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgo nas phan pa ci 'grub bgyis shing /
NK036(chi)032:929: mdor na dma' ba'i sa bzung /
NK036(chi)032:931: dka' thub dang bcud len la brten gyin phyogs mtha'
NK036(chi)032:932: dag tu bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen mkhas btsun
NK036(chi)032:933: bzang gsum bzhugs zer ba rnams kyi zhabs drung du
NK036(chi)032:934: phyin nas gdams pa'i rtsa gdar bcad cing /
NK036(chi)032:935: mchims phu la sogs pa'i dben gnas khyad par can
NK036(chi)032:936: rnams su sgrub pa nan tan snying por byas pas
NK036(chi)032:937: / de dang mthun pa'i byin rlabs dang yon tan kyang mtshon re skyes pa lags pas /
NK036(chi)032:938: da phyin chad bdag gi rjes su 'jug pa'i bu slob rnams kyang /
NK036(chi)032:939: yar bla ma dkon mchog la mos gus /
NK036(chi)032:940: mnyam par gyur pa rnams la dag pa'i snang ba /
NK036(chi)032:941: dman par gyur pa rnams la pha ma'i 'du shes kyis phyogs ris med pa'i byams pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:942: snying rje byang chub sems zung du chud pa'i sgo nas phan pa rgya cher sgrub pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:943: gzhan yang bla ma dang chos la phyogs ris dang bdag bzung mi mdzad par /
NK036(chi)032:944: mkhas shing grub pa brnyes pa'i bla ma dam pa rnams bsten /
NK036(chi)032:946: bsam pas nang gi sgro 'dogs gcod cing /
NK036(chi)032:947: sgom pas phyi nang gsang gsum gyi sgro 'dogs thams cad chod par byas nas /
NK036(chi)032:948: dben pa'i gnas su sgrub pa nan tan snying por mdzod cig /
NK036(chi)032:949: de ltar mdzad pas bla ma'i byin rlabs rgyud la zhugs /
NK036(chi)032:950: yi dam mkha' 'gros byin gyis brlabs pa'i dus su
NK036(chi)032:951: gzhan don byed pa la lus ngag yid gsum gyi
NK036(chi)032:952: gyong dang / skye bo log sgrub la sogs bzod pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:953: rang don gyi 'khris ma zhugs pa mdzad nas /
NK036(chi)032:954: bstan pa rin po che'i khur chen po bsnams pa dang /
NK036(chi)032:955: bla ma dam pa rnams kyi phyag srol mi nyams shing /
NK036(chi)032:956: thugs dgongs rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir du 'jig rten
NK036(chi)032:957: tshe 'di'i chos dang mthun pa'i bya ba ci dang
NK036(chi)032:958: ci yin pa thams cad ring du dor ba dang
NK036(chi)032:959: / chos dang mthun pa'i bya ba gang la'ang brtson pas skyo ngal dang /
NK036(chi)032:960: phyogs ris med pa'i sgo nas 'gro ba sems can
NK036(chi)032:961: gyi don rgya chen po bsgrub par brtson pa thugs
NK036(chi)032:963: tshul 'di nyid rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po
NK036(chi)032:964: nam mkha'i snying pos byin gyis brlabs pa'i ku su
NK036(chi)032:965: lu'i bya bral ba shes rab rgya mtshos /
NK036(chi)032:966: bla ma rdor bsam bla ma nam rin bla ma sangs rgyas rgyal mtshan rnams kyis bskul ba'i ngor /
NK036(chi)032:967: stag gi lo zla ba brgyad pa'i tshes bcu gsum
NK036(chi)032:968: la babs pas sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das nas
NK036(chi)032:969: lo sum stong bzhi brgya nyi shu rtsa drug song
